title: The Outer Limits- O.B.I.T (S01E07)
description:
"O.B.I.T." is an episode of the original The Outer Limits television show. It first aired on 4 November 1963, during the first season.

	In this room, twenty four hours a day, seven days a week, security personnel at the defense department Cyprus Hill's Research Center keep constant watch on its scientists through O.B.I.T., a mysterious electronic device whose very existence was carefully kept from the public at large.
